            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1276720</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Leica 宣布推出两款全新产品：M11 黑漆版相机及 Noctilux-M 50 f/1.2 ASPH. 黑漆版镜头。两款产品的设计展现 Leica 的标志性风格外，展示 Leica 数十年来独特的美学理念及精湛工艺。</p><h4></h4><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276727" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-1-694x520.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-1-694x520.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-1-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276729" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-2-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-2-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-scaled.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>新款 Leica M11 黑漆版采用黄铜材质的顶盖、拨盘及开关均覆以亮黑色漆面，搭配顶盖上的「Leica」字样及亮银色镀铬快门按钮。快门拨盘及 ISO 拨盘上用上交叉滚花纹理。相机去掉了传统的红点标志，带来更低调的外观设计。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-3-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276730" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-3-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-3-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-4-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276731" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-4-694x520.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-4-694x520.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20230_leica_m11_glos-4-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>Leica 的 M 系列经典黑漆面自 1962 年首次应用于 Leica M3，深受摄影爱好者热烈追捧。这种漆面随时间使用，会逐渐显露出黄铜色，形成独特的光泽效果，为每台相机留下专属于其使用者的故事。</p><h4></h4><p>黑漆版 Noctilux-M 50 f/1.2 ASPH. 镜头则专为搭配亮黑漆面的 M 相机而设计。该镜头以大光圈及独特焦外成像效果著称，并附有圆形遮光罩及亮黑漆面前后镜头盖，红色「英尺」刻度更增添复古韵味。这款镜头重新演绎了 Noctilux 系列的经典特质，为摄影师带来极佳的画质表现。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276732" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-scaled.jpg 1199w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276734" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-1-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Leica 同时推出了一系列高级配件，包括沙丘灰色版的可调节背带、M11 保护套及相机包，均以高品质牛皮制成，进一步完善 M 系统的使用体验。</p><h4></h4><p>Leica M11 黑漆版的建议零售价为港币 75,900，而 Noctilux-M 50 f/1.2 ASPH. 黑漆版则为港币 69,500。两款产品现已于全球 Leica 专卖店、官方网上渠道及授权经销商发售。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/11731_noctiluxm_1_25-1-scaled.jpg"><br /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24040_systemtaschem_-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276735" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24040_systemtaschem_-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24040_systemtaschem_-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24040_systemtaschem_-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24040_systemtaschem_-scaled.jpg 1199w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24041_protector_taup-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276736" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24041_protector_taup-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24041_protector_taup-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/24041_protector_taup-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/18574_tragriemenm_ta-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276737" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/18574_tragriemenm_ta-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/18574_tragriemenm_ta-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/18574_tragriemenm_ta-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><div class="page" title="Page 4"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><p>Leica 香港铜锣湾旗舰店<br />
地址:铜锣湾白沙道 12 号地舖<br />
联络电话: 2385 0118</p></div></div></div><p>资料来源：Leica</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/23/leica-m11-noctilux-m-50-f-1-2-asph/dc/">黑漆版 Leica M11 + Noctilux-M 50 f/1.2 ASPH. 推出，展现经典设计与黑漆机身工艺</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
